  "title": "Property, Finance & Administration Officer",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an Property, Finance & Administration Officer to join our team. This role is essential for ensuring the smooth functioning of our office and events' administration, operations, accounts and financial matters as well as property management.</p><ul><li><p>Handle property and tenant administration, including invoicing, arrears follow-up and utility billing</p></li><li><p>Coordinate building maintenance, repairs, contractors, cleaners and pest control services</p></li><li><p>Oversee office, hall and room bookings, usage coordination and event support</p></li><li><p>Manage daily office administration, correspondence, records and general enquiries</p></li><li><p>Support finance administration such as payments, petty cash, banking-in and record-keeping</p></li><li><p>Assist with meetings, events, membership matters and general operational support</p></li><li><p>Provide administrative and operational support to management, committees and team members<br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /><br />- Chinese organisation staff knowledge of Mandarin and English are essential.<br />- 5.5 working days per week</p></li></ul>",
